<HEADLINE>
GUIDES AT TALIESIN WEST GIVE INSIGHT TO GREAT ARCHITECT OF 20TH
CENTURY 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By BARBARA YOST  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
