<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-R-GUNS-POLITICS-REVIEW-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE GUN DEBATE HAS TWO SIDES. NOW, A THIRD WAY. 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(DW) 
 By DAVID E. ROSENBAUM   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ The Senate made a bit of history last week, passing
gun-control legislation that had been left for dead a week before.
</P>
<P>
   The measures are modest, which may suggest that anti-gun-control
