<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-24 16:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9225 &Cx1f; sci-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SCI-WATCH-NYT &LR;      05-24 0690
