<P>
   KOSOVO-BELGRADE (Belgrade) _ Widespread blackouts and loss of
water are seriously disrupting the lives of people in the Yugoslav
capital. Things have gotten so bad that in the Belgrade suburb of
Zemun, even McDonald's didn't have water for coffee. By Steven
Erlanger.
</P>
