   HOWARD-COMPLAINTS (Santa Clarita, Calif.) _ When Santa
Clarita-based Howard and Phil's closed shop this month, it gave
many of its employees no warning and, weeks later, some are filing
complaints with the labor board to get their last month of pay. By
Jason Takenouchi.
</P>
