<P>
   BURBANK-AIRPORT (Burbank, Calif.) _ In a major development in
the fight over a new terminal at Burbank Airport, the Airport
Authority board met Monday and proposed building a smaller terminal
than the one it had proposed. By Michael Coit. (Will move in the
``n'' California news file.)
</P>
