<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-24 19:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9471 &Cx1f; tth-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-TV-HOME-SPI &LR;      05-24 0316
