<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-24 21:35 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9609 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-LATIN-PRESS-NYT &LR;      05-24 0335
