   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, May 12,
about Cox Communications' acquisition of TCA Cable TV misstated the
scope of a previous agreement by Cox, involving Media General. Cox
purchased Media General's cable operations in northern Virginia,
not the entire company.
