Christopher Mason, author of ``Undressed: The Life and Times of
Gianni Versace.'' The book's publisher Little, Brown, dropped
publication of Mason's unauthorized biography. The cancellation has
raised questions about the kinds of pressure, legal and otherwise,
that a powerful fashion house can bring to bear on a publisher, an
author, and his sources. Little, Brown denies it was pressured into
cancelling publication of the book. (Barbara Alper/New York Times
Photo) LITE
