those who have read them: China has stolen data on every
significant American nuclear warhead, the stolen secrets helped
China design and test modern nuclear weapons, and Chinese espionage
at the biggest government weapons labs is long-standing and
continuing. (Paul Hosefros/New York Times Photo)
