<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-24 22:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9655 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-EDIT-OBSERVER-NYT &LR;      05-24 0627
