<P>
   &QL; 
WICKENBURG (Wickenburg, Ariz.) _ As the cowboy ambled to the
counter to pick up his store-bought lariat, the sweet smell of
leather and oil wafted through the warm air of Ben's Saddlery shop.
Old Wickenburg. That's what longtime boot and saddlemaker Arlene
